        {
          "id": 1621279199080,
          "type": "text",
          "content": "\"<h2>Mangroves</h2><p><strong>The ROPME region has limited mangrove area (about 0.1% of the global total). </strong></p><p><br></p><p>As of 2016, the region had 168 km² of mangrove forest.</p>\""
        }
